tossup_question: -  Energy –  What is the name of the prediction in classical physics that incorrectly proposed that an ideal black body at thermal equilibrium will emit increasingly higher frequencies of radiation with infinite power?
bonus_question: -  Energy –  What is the primary energy carrier that is synthesized in the Krebs Cycle and is one of the most common reducing agents in the cell?
bonus_answer: ANSWER: NADH OR NICOTINAMIDE ADENINE DINUCLEOTIDE (DO NOT ACCEPT: NAD+)
